game.name: Goblin Flying Machine
game.description:
The crazy flying goblin has reached out to you for help! Would you like to give your helping hands to this different creature on her unique adventure? Join Goblin Flying Machine and be prepared to guide him to go as high as possible! This creature has a dream to fly high and he knows that you are the only person who could help make her dream come true. Practice hard and learn fast how to handle her in this brand new adventure game!

It is not as agile or intelligent as a bird or powerful as a plane, so you would have to take care of her flying moves on your own. Guide him to grab the stars while avoiding all the obstacles that you see in the sky! Make sure that she collects all the needful machine parts and do not forget to upgrade her wings to allow her stand straight against all the tricky challenges. Keep her away from the deadly airships, birds and unicorns that you see along the way!

Launch her fast to reach new heights while being focused on collecting as many cog-shaped tokens as possible in this HTML5 flying game! Try to make her climb in the air and grab the powerful wings to fly high and score big! Do not bother if you fail initially as you would have plenty of attempts to play and make your new best score without download. Our wider collection of free adventure challenges makes sure that you would find new fun and thrill every time you visit us at atmegame.com.
